## 5. Third-Party Assets

This project includes third-party assets (e.g., sounds, textures) which are subject to the following licenses:

- **Sounds**: Some sound effects used in this project are provided by [Pixabay](https://pixabay.com/sound-effects/) and are licensed under the [Pixabay License](https://pixabay.com/service/license-summary/). While credit is not required, we acknowledge their contribution to the project. These sound effects cannot be redistributed as standalone files.

- **Textures**: Some textures were created using [Canva](https://www.canva.com/). These textures are licensed under Canva’s [Free License](https://www.canva.com/policies/content-license-agreement/), and cannot be redistributed or resold as standalone assets.

Please review the original licensing terms for each asset if you intend to reuse or modify them outside the scope of this project.

